      • SoundEffectInfo

        public SoundEffectInfo​(String uid,
                       String type,
                       String mode,
                       String name)
        A parameterized constructor used to create a SoundEffectInfo instance.
        Parameters:
        uid - Indicates a sound effect ID.
        type - Indicates a sound effect type, which can be SoundEffect#SOUND_EFFECT_TYPE_EC, SoundEffect#SOUND_EFFECT_TYPE_GC, or SoundEffect#SOUND_EFFECT_TYPE_NS.
        mode - Indicates a sound effect mode, which can be SoundEffect#SOUND_EFFECT_MODE_AUXILIARY, SoundEffect#SOUND_EFFECT_MODE_INSERT, or SoundEffect#SOUND_EFFECT_MODE_PRE_PROCESSING.
        name - Indicates the name of a sound effect.
        Since:
        1
